Me and mom have always shared a love for designing clothes and there’s nothing more special than creating something from scratch! 
From selecting the perfect fabric to bringing our vision to life, it’s a journey we truly enjoy. 
This time, a big thanks to @suryanshfab_official for being a part of it. Their fabric collection is absolutely amazing and perfect for the festive season ahead. If you’re planning to create something unique, do check them out!
